## 8. Premium Access & Razorpay Payment Integration

Users can buy a premium upgrade: **₹25 for Lifetime Premium Color Panel Access & 6 Months Ad-Free Gameplay**.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Player (Client)
    participant Server as Node.js Express Server
    participant Gateway as Razorpay API

    User->>Server: POST /api/payment/order (authenticated)
    Server->>Gateway: Create Order (amount = 2500 paise, currency = "INR")
    Gateway-->>Server: Return order_id
    Server-->>User: Return order_id & keys
    User->>User: Launch Razorpay Checkout Modal
    User->>Gateway: Submit payment credentials
    Gateway-->>User: Return payment details (payment_id, signature)
    User->>Server: POST /api/payment/verify (payment_id, order_id, signature)
    Note over Server: Cryptographic check:<br/>HmacSHA256(order_id + "|" + payment_id, secret) == signature
    Server->>Server: Set has_premium = 1 and ad_free_until = Date.now() + 6 months in DB
    Server-->>User: HTTP 200 Success (Unlock Granted)
```

### 8.1 API Endpoints
* **`POST /api/payment/order`**:
  - Requires valid JWT token in Header.
  - Server invokes Razorpay Orders API:
    ```javascript
    const options = {
      amount: 2500, // ₹25.00 in paise
      currency: "INR",
      receipt: `receipt_user_${user.id}`
    };
    const order = await razorpay.orders.create(options);
    res.json({ success: true, orderId: order.id, amount: order.amount });
    ```
* **`POST /api/payment/verify`**:
  - Requires valid JWT token in Header.
  - Payload: `{ razorpay_payment_id, razorpay_order_id, razorpay_signature }`.
  - Verifies payment authenticity, updates database flags:
    ```javascript
    const crypto = require("crypto");
    const hmac = crypto.createHmac("sha256", process.env.RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET);
    hmac.update(razorpay_order_id + "|" + razorpay_payment_id);
    const generated_signature = hmac.digest("hex");
    
    if (generated_signature === razorpay_signature) {
      // Payment successful!
      await db.updateUserPremium(user.id, {
        has_premium: 1,
        ad_free_until: new Date(Date.now() + 6 * 30 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000) // 6 months
      });
      res.json({ success: true, message: "Premium unlocked!" });
    } else {
      res.status(400).json({ success: false, error: "Signature verification failed" });
    }
    ```

